cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.DS, cs.SE 

Reasoning: 

1. cs.AI - The paper deals with reasoning and planning, which are core topics in artificial intelligence. 
2. cs.LO - The paper discusses soundness and completeness of the proposed approximation, which is related to logic and reasoning. 
3. cs.PL - The paper presents an answer set programming based planner, which falls under the category of declarative programming and logic programming. 
4. cs.DS - The paper deals with the complexity of the conditional planning problem, which is related to computational complexity and algorithms. 
5. cs.SE - The paper presents experimental results comparing the proposed planner to other planners, which is related to software engineering and empirical software engineering.
